Class RdfIOException

          com.twiddles.ganesha.functionality.RdfIOException
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class RdfIOException
extends java.lang.Exception

An exception during input or output of RDF/XML data. This exception is designed to enable implementations of RDFFile to report common RDF/XML file read and write errors to Ganesha's GUI so that they may be handled in a sensible way. (For example: alerting the user)
